'''Osgiliath, Västerås Tolkiensällskap''' is the Swedish Tolkien Society of [[wikipedia:Västerås|Västerås]]. As of 2024, the association seems to be inactive ([http://www.hacke.saeab.se/osgiliath/calendar.html their calendar] doesn't show events past 2009).

Activities in Osgiliath are said to involve live role-playing, sword fighting, studying the works and languages of [[J.R.R. Tolkien]], medieval dancing, handicraft, etc.
